			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				Troll SK's rock..they just take a long time to level (worst EXP penalty in the game)but at high levels they are lethal.Mages are great also due to their pets...shamans kick arse IMO.Theres no ONE good class to play.Any class can become lethal in the right hands.when it boils down to it play a class you ENJOY the most.Screw stats. <br>  <br> Heres some basic PVP tips: <br>  <br> *When in battle, CHANGE YOUR VIEW alot.People love to sneak up on ya when your low on HP and have a mob slapping you around. <br>  <br> *CARRY A PUMICESTONE!As a melee your life will be much less difficult with a pumice stone on ya. (costs around 20pp and has 5 charges of nullify magic-negates root,most DOT's,etc..) <br>  <br> *KEEP MOVING.If a wiz is on ya blasting get right up on him and start hacking away.Dont try to outcast a caster.If it looks grim...buckle down and bite the bullet..(or run and zone..depending on your play style) <br>  <br> *most battles will be determined by who attacks who first.Try to GET THE UPPER HAND.Level in safe areas you know well.PVP when your ready...on YOUR terms. <br>  <br> I know i left alot out but I'm getting carpal tunnel syndrome...Please add on what im missing..		

